OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FThe war in Iran has left hundreds of
OL,7,Fthousands of British citizens stranded
OL,8,Fin the Middle East, as airspaces are
OL,9,Fclosed across the region.
OL,11,FThe renewed fighting hasn't just
OL,12,Faffected those trying to leave the
OL,13,Farea, but the millions of passengers
OL,14,Fthat travel through major transport
OL,15,Fhubs like Dubai Airport each year, as
OL,16,Fthey connect flights from Europe,
OL,17,FAsia, Australasia and Africa.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
