PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772568683
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FAs the conflict widens to countries
OL,7,Fincluding Cyprus, where an RAF site
OL,8,Fwas the target of a drone attack, many
OL,9,Fare questioning whether it is safe to
OL,10,Ftravel to areas that could be
OL,11,Fpotential targets of strikes.
OL,13,FSo what restrictions are in place, and
OL,14,Fwhat is the advice for those hoping to
OL,15,Ftravel?
OL,17,FThe Middle East
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772568683
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FAs of Tuesday, there are multiple
OL,7,Fcountries that have restrictions in
OL,8,Fplace. Of these, the majority have a
OL,9,Ftotal closure of airspace, meaning it
OL,10,Fis incredibly difficult to travel in
OL,11,For out of the countries:
OL,13,FOthers have a partial closure, meaning
OL,14,Ftravel is still heavily restricted:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772568683
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FDespite airspaces only being partially
OL,7,Fclosed in Saudi Arabia and the United
OL,8,FArab Emirates, very few flights are
OL,9,Fleaving the countries' airports for
OL,10,Fthe UK. Airlines have said the
OL,11,Fsituation is being closely monitored
OL,12,Fand could be subject to change.
OL,14,FSome airlines have advised passengers
OL,15,Fnot to attend the airport unless they
OL,16,Fhave been contacted directly, and to
OL,17,Fkeep across the latest travel updates
OL,18,Fon the airlines' websites.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
