CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772568683
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FBritish nationals in Bahrain, Israel,
OL,7,FKuwait, Palestine, Qatar and the
OL,8,FUnited Arab Emirates are advised by
OL,9,Fthe Government to register their
OL,10,Fpresence in the region, in order to
OL,11,Freceive direct updates from the
OL,12,FForeign, Commonwealth and Development
OL,13,FOffice (FCDO).
OL,15,FYou should also continue to follow the
OL,16,Ftravel advice for the country you are
OL,17,Fin, and keep up to date with advice
OL,18,Ffrom the local authorities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
