PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772568683
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FHoliday destinations like Turkey,
OL,12,FEgypt and Cyprus are largely
OL,13,Funaffected and remain open, as the
OL,14,Fmajority of airstrikes remain centred
OL,15,Faround the Gulf.
OL,17,FHowever, travellers are advised to
OL,18,Fstay vigilant to any changing travel
OL,19,Fcircumstances and keep up to date with
OL,20,Fadvice from the foreign office.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772568683
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FAs of Tuesday, foreign office advice
OL,7,Ffor Turkey remains unchanged for
OL,8,Ftravellers arriving from the UK, and
OL,9,Fareas with popular holiday resorts are
OL,10,Fnot affected by the conflict in the
OL,11,FGulf.
OL,13,FFlights are still operating between
OL,14,FTurkey and the UK, but passengers
OL,15,Fshould check the airline's latest
OL,16,Fadvice before leaving for the airport,
OL,17,Fas the situation could change rapidly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772568683
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FThe government does warn that regional
OL,7,Fescalation poses significant security
OL,8,Frisks and has led to travel
OL,9,Fdisruption. Travellers are advised to
OL,10,Ffamiliarise themselves with the
OL,11,FGovernment's guidance on "how to
OL,12,Fprepare for a crisis", follow advice
OL,13,Ffrom authorities, and ensure their
OL,14,Ftravel documents are up to date.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
