PN,30910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772568683
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FA drone attack on the RAF Akrotiri
OL,7,Fbase on Monday led to some cancelled
OL,8,Fflights and is a lesson in how quickly
OL,9,Fa situation can evolve.
OL,11,FHowever, the FCDO is not advising
OL,12,Fagainst travel to Cyprus, although
OL,13,Fholidaymakers should be aware that the
OL,14,Fescalating situation in the area poses
OL,15,Fsignificant security risks.
OL,17,FBritish travellers should familiarise
OL,18,Fthemselves with the FCDO's
OL,19,Finstructions on what to do in a
OL,20,Fcrisis, as well as ensuring they have
OL,21,Fvalid travel documents and insurance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772568683
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FThere have been a number of flight
OL,7,Fcancellations to and from Cyprus,
OL,8,Fparticularly since the drone attack on
OL,9,Fthe RAF base, so passengers should
OL,10,Fstay notified of any updates from
OL,11,Ftheir airline.
OL,13,FWhat travel protections are you
OL,14,Fentitled to?
OL,16,FWhile the foreign office still deems
OL,17,Fareas in Turkey, Egypt and Cyprus safe
OL,18,Fto travel and tourism continues,
OL,19,Fdisruption is still very possible.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
