OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772568683
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FUnder UK law, if you are departing
OL,7,Ffrom an airport in the UK on any
OL,8,Fairline, or arriving at an EU or UK
OL,9,Fairport on an EU or UK airline, you
OL,10,Fhave legal rights if your flight is
OL,11,Fcancelled.
OL,13,FYour airline is legally required to
OL,14,Foffer you an alternative flight at the
OL,15,Fearliest opportunity or a full refund
OL,16,Fif your flight is cancelled.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772568683
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FHowever, you may not be entitled to
OL,7,Fadditional compensation, as
OL,8,Fcancellations relating to war will
OL,9,Ffall under "extraordinary
OL,10,Fcircumstances."
OL,12,FIf the delay for a new flight is over
OL,13,Ftwo hours, the airline must provide
OL,14,Fyou with care and support, such as
OL,15,Fmeals and refreshments, or hotel
OL,16,Faccommodation and transport to the
OL,17,Faccommodation if an overnight stay is
OL,18,Fwarranted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772568683
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FIf your flight to the UK is cancelled
OL,7,Fand you are travelling with a non-UK
OL,8,For non-EU airline, you are not covered
OL,9,Funder this legislation and will have
OL,10,Fto check the local airline laws and
OL,11,Fpolicies.
OL,13,FIf you booked a package holiday
OL,14,Fthrough a UK tour operator and the
OL,15,FFCDO deems your location unsafe, or
OL,16,Fflight delays and cancellations mean
OL,17,Fyou can't attend, then your operator
OL,18,Fmust offer an alternative holiday if
OL,19,Fpossible or refund you the full price.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
